{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shui's Odyssey is a narrative-driven puzzle game that tightly integrates storytelling and gameplay. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Experience the passage of time for three generations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will join the protagonist, &quot;Xiao Shui,&quot; on a profound journey to rediscover lost memories and embark on a soul-searching quest. Through  themes of love, family, and friendship, players will uncover emotional  chapters of life set against the backdrop of a significant era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/store1.png?t=1738910281\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Imaginative visual puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the game unfolds, players will encounter a series of intricate visual illusions, akin to the unveiling of a scroll, gradually revealing the truth behind the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/shui_gif_new1.gif?t=1738910281\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Exquisite original hand-drawn illustrations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring a wealth of delicate and stunning artwork and animations, a script inspired by real-life experiences, and meticulously designed gameplay mechanics, Shui's Odyssey offers a captivating gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/store2.png?t=1738910281\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Endless Learning","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2808960/299f746bdabb0611415400ff16eeb6e2470a862a.jpg"},{"name":"Progressing Smoothly","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2808960/e2ab0fd3197f380eca0669cd7aca8fd813aa0b08.jpg"